des: Sam Huff grounds out, shortstop Orlando Arcia to first baseman Matt Olson.
Sam Huff singles on a ground ball to third baseman Austin Riley.   Brad Miller to 2nd.
Sam Huff walks.   Jonah Heim to 2nd.

Sam Huff grounds into a force out, first baseman Ryan Noda to shortstop Nick Allen.   Jonah Heim scores.    Leody Taveras out at 2nd.    Sam Huff to 1st.
